      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jetrus fazzija : Sla-\nwehts lai irr tas KUNGS / kas\njuhs irr isglahbis no to Egipternu\nRohkas/un no Warais Rohkas/\nkas tohs Laudis irr ispestijs no to\nEgipternu Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu atsihstu es / ka tas\nKUNGS seelaks irr/ ne ka wiſſi\nDeewi / tapehz ka tre Lepnibu\nprett winnu irr dsinnufchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad rehine Jetrus/ Moh-\nsus Tehwozis/ Dedsamus-łippu-\nens / un lippurus preekſch Dee-\nwa/ un Aarons un wisfee Israeka\nWezzajee nahze Maisti ehst ar\nMohsus Tehwozi preekſch Deewa\nWaigu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ohtra Deena apfehdahs\nMohsus/ tohs Laudis teefahrt/ un\ntee Laudis stahiweja preekſch Moh-\nsus no Rihtalihs Wakkaram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Mohsus Tehwo-\nzis wiſſu redſeja / fo winſch teem\nLaudim darrija / fazzija winſch :\nkas tas tahds Darbs / fo tu to\nLauschu deht darrees ? tapehz tu\nweenâ pats ſehd/ un wiſſi Laudis\nstahiw preekſch teiw/ no Rihta lihds\nWakkaram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Mohsus us fatwu\nTehwozi : tapehz ka tee Laudis\npee man nahk Deewu waiznaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad teem kahda Leeta irr/\ntad nahk tee pee mannis / un es\nteeſaju ſarp weenu un ſarp oh-\ntru/ un darri teem finnamus tahs\nDeewaLikkumus un winna Bau-\nhbu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Mohs\nwozis us winnu : ta ne i\nLeeta/ fo tu darri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu gurtin pagurſt\nbi tu/ ka arridsan tee Laud\npee tew irr / jo ſchi Leeta\nwiſſai gruhta / tu weens\nspehj to padarriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nu klausi mann\nfni / es dohſchn tew Pa-\ntad Deews buhs ar tewin\ntu to Lauschudeht Deew-\nfchâ / un nenefs tahs\npreekſch Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un mahzi teem tob\nmus untahs Bauslibas/\nteem finnamu to Jettu /\nteem irr ja-eet/ un to Dar-\nteem ja-darra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tu luho peh\ngeemun Deewabihjatigee\nreem / pehz taiſneem W\nkas toRegantibu eenihst fi\nfeem Laudim/ un eezell pa\nAhwerstus/ Kapteines/\nkus pahr peezdefiniteem/ u\nneekus pahr definiteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka teem buhs tob\nwisfa Laika teefahrt / bet\nta irr/ ka tee wiſſas gruh-\ntas tew preekſcha ness/ u\nmasakas Leetas lai tee pa-\nfa/ atweeglinajeeg ta pats\ntee tew palihds nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tu tahs Leetas\ntad ir Deews tew parweh-\ntu warri pastahweht / i\nſchee Laudis nahks us fatw-\ntu ar Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mohsus klaufij\n"
    }
  ],
